{
  "arquivo": "ca02_09",
  "total": 40,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Phew...\\nDinner's over, so all that's left is to go to bed.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Since we arrived in Okinawa and started our sightseeing tour I \\n feel fulfilled. Visiting the power spots and experiencing the \\n exquisite Okinawan cuisine...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I wonder if it's because I had a lot on my mind,\\n but my eyes feel unusually alert.\\n Will I be able to sleep at all?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hm?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Who is it?\\n Even though it's already time to sleep...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yes?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Good evening, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino?!\\nIs something wrong? It's late.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Well, um...\\nI came to say goodnight.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "O-oh, right.\\nI see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Well, I can't sleep.\\nAre you going to sleep, Futaro?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, actually, I was also thinking\\nthat I'm strangely awake, and wouldn't\\nbe able to sleep. We're the same, hahaha...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Now this situation is strange. Nino wants to say something,\\n and it's just the two of us right now. This is bad...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(She said she came to say goodnight,\\n so it's already over, right?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Is it possible...that she wants to spend the night with me?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(No, no! That's not allowed!\\n We're still minors, and if our parents find out,\\n it'll be a huge problem!!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "H-hey?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What is it...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...do you wanna be with me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WHA%p-2;――%p;?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Be with her... Does she mean...?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "W-wait, Nino.\\nI do want to be with you, but, um...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I'm glad. I was a little worried\\nthat maybe I was the only one who felt that way.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Th-then... I...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(What kind of choice am I being forced to make?\\n Is my rationality being tested?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But still! I can't bring Nino back to my room\\n this late at night!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Futaro?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino, you should probably go back to your room soon.\\nIchika's got to be worried about you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I should head back now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "See you tomorrow. Goodnight.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Goodnight, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Holy moly...\\nHer actions take a toll on my heart...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Honestly, I like her!\\n But I'm not sure my heart can take it!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}